{
  "page": "Viserys Targaryen (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Viserys Targaryen</b> is the name of several members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>. These include: \n</p>\n<ul><li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen_(son_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen (son of Aenys I)\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, second son of King Aenys I Targaryen and Queen Alyssa Velaryon.</li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a>, fifth king of the Seven Kingdoms succeeding his grandfather, King Jaehaerys I Targaryen.</li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys II Targaryen\">Viserys II Targaryen</a>, tenth king of the Seven Kingdoms. Prior to being king he was the Hand of the King to his brother Aegon III and to his nephews Daeron I and Baelor I.</li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, styling himself as Viserys, the third of his name, called the <i>Beggar King</i>, second son of Aerys II, who was forced into exile after Robert's Rebellion.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Feminine_equivalent\">Feminine equivalent</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Viserys_Targaryen_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Feminine equivalent\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Viserra_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserra Targaryen\">Viserra Targaryen</a>, tenth child and sixth daughter of King Jaehaerys I and Queen Alysanne Targaryen.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Viserys_Targaryen_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys\" title=\"Viserys\">Viserys</a> (disambiguation)</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403150711\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 7/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:7173-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403150711 and revision id 322897\n -->\n",
